sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Browser)
    participant A as REST API
    participant D as PostgreSQL
    participant R as Redis

    Note over C,R: Login Flow
    C->>A: POST /auth/login {email, password}
    A->>R: Check rate limit (rl:ip:login)
    A->>D: SELECT user by email
    D-->>A: User record
    A->>A: bcrypt.compare(password)
    A->>A: Generate JWT (15min, RS256)
    A->>A: Generate refresh token
    A->>D: INSERT refresh_token (hash)
    A->>D: INSERT audit_log (user.login)
    A-->>C: 200 {accessToken, refreshToken, user}

    Note over C,R: Token Refresh Flow
    C->>A: POST /auth/refresh {refreshToken}
    A->>D: SELECT refresh_token by hash
    D-->>A: Token record
    A->>A: Validate expiry, not revoked
    A->>D: DELETE old refresh_token
    A->>A: Generate new JWT + refresh token
    A->>D: INSERT new refresh_token (hash)
    A-->>C: 200 {accessToken, refreshToken}

    Note over C,R: Logout Flow
    C->>A: POST /auth/logout {refreshToken}
    A->>D: SET revoked_at on refresh_token
    A->>D: INSERT audit_log (user.logout)
    A-->>C: 204 No Content
